# LinkActionButton

A Link Action Button is a button that appear as highlighted words or images and take users to another page or screen.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/link-action-button
```

```tsx
import { LinkActionButton } from '@ids-ts/link-action-button';
```

## Props API

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `automationId` | `string` | No | ID for automation tests |
| `size` | `LinkActionButtonSize` | Yes | - |
| `weight` | `LinkActionButtonWeight` | No | - |
| `alignment` | `'left' | 'right'` | No | - |
| `innerRef` | `| ((instance: HTMLButtonElement | null) => void...` | No | Function to return innerRef |
| `variant` | `LinkActionButtonVariant` | No | - |

<details>
<summary>Full TypeScript Interface</summary>

```typescript
export interface LinkActionButtonProps extends ThemeableElement<'button'> {
  /** ID for automation tests */
  automationId?: string;
  /**
   * Specifies Button size, 'extraSmall', 'small' or 'medium'
   *
   * @default 'small'
   */
  size: LinkActionButtonSize;
  /**
   * variation for font weights
   *
   * @default 'medium'
   */
  weight?: LinkActionButtonWeight;
  /**
   * provide alignment for Link Action Button
   *
   * @default 'right'
   */
  alignment?: 'left' | 'right';
  /** Function to return innerRef */
  innerRef?:
    | ((instance: HTMLButtonElement | null) => void)
    | React.RefObject<HTMLButtonElement>
    | null
    | undefined;
  /** Determines the type of link, primary or secondary
   *
   * @default standalone
   */
  variant?: LinkActionButtonVariant;
}

export type LinkActionButtonSize = 'extraSmall' | 'small' | 'medium';

export type LinkActionButtonWeight = 'regular' | 'medium' | 'demi';

export type LinkActionButtonVariant = 'standalone' | 'secondary';
```

</details>

